title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Optical, Photo & Cinema Graphics & Related Ac
description: Imports Intra Eu - Optical, Photo & Cinema Graphics & Related Ac in the United Kingdom decreased to 811.08 GBP Million in September from 884.02 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Optical, Photo & Cinema Graphic in the United Kingdom averaged 433.89 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 884.02 GBP Million in August of 2022 and a record low of 181.15 GBP Million in April of 1996.
